Proposed law provides that the reproduction of written documentation shall be made
available at no cost to the survivor and may only be released at the direction of the survivor
who is a competent adult. Further provides that the release of this documentation to the
survivor does not invalidate the survivor's reasonable expectation of privacy and is not a
